%20%3Cstrong%3Ewill.i.am%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cstrong%3EBridgewater%20Associates%20founder%20Ray%20Dalio%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBenioff%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20AI%20a%20basic%20human%20right%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20question%20and%20the%20venue%20in%20which%20he%20asked%20it%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fancy%20lunch%20at%20Davos%20with%20Salesforce%20clients%20and%20global%20luminaries%20%E2%80%94%20epitomized%20the%20polarized%20and%20multilayered%20debates%20about%20this%20technology.%20Some%20see%20it%20as%20a%20powerful%20universal%20good%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20even%20a%20basic%20human%20right.%20Others%20see%20it%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20humanity%20on%20multiple%20levels.%20Maybe%20it's%20a%20bit%20of%20both.%20Whatever%20it%20is%2C%20it's%20coming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20companies%20are%20going%20to%20capitalize%20on%20it%2C%20some%20will%20try%20and%20fail.%20Salesforce%20is%20one%20company%20that%20is%20already%20making%20it%20happen%20in%20practice%20with%20its%20%26quot%3Bagentforce%26quot%3B%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20struck%20me%20at%20Davos%20that%20I%20didn't%20fully%20understand%20before%20is%20that%20the%20tech%20world%20sees%20AI%20%26quot%3Bagents%26quot%3B%20as%20full-time%20workers%20who%20will%20work%20side%20by%20side%20with%20people%2C%20not%20just%20tools%20to%20help%20people.%20Benioff%20said%20this%20current%20generation%20of%20CEOs%20will%20be%20the%20last%20to%20manage%20%26quot%3Bexclusively%20human%20workforces.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20AI%20agents%2C%20he%20said%2C%20institutions%20will%20need%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20humans%20and%20AI%20%26quot%3Bcreate%20success%20together.%26quot%3B%20More%20on%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fagentic-ai-employees-ceos-managers-bots-davos-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20my%20colleagues%20Hugh%20Langley%20and%20Spriha%20Srivastava.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94%20Jamie%20Heller%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227dd05002-a859-48dd-a18f-41c1338fe291%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFOBO%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20of%20this%20might%20have%20you%20feeling%20a%20term%20bobbing%20around%20the%20conference%2C%20FOBO%20%E2%80%94%20fear%20of%20being%20obsolete.%20To%20be%20sure%2C%20there%20is%20always%20sand%20in%20the%20wheels%20that%20slows%20these%20trends%20down.%20Some%20people%20with%20whom%20I%20spoke%20said%20they%20felt%20paralyzed%20by%20choice%2C%20with%20so%20many%20vendors%20pitching%20their%20AI%20wares.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20these%20services%20are%20costly%20%E2%80%94%20sellers%20need%20to%20persuade%20buyers%20the%20benefits%20are%20worth%20it.%20But%20one%20way%20or%20another%2C%20change%20is%20coming.%20And%20we'll%20do%20our%20best%20at%20BI%20to%20keep%20you%20informed%20on%20what%20can%20help%20you.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94%20Jamie%20Heller%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a9705c07-40f4-49f2-ad2c-d1a775cd4a8a%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20that%20AI%20investment%20could%20pay%20off%20this%20year%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20real%20belief%20that%20we'll%20start%20to%20see%20a%20return%20on%20those%20AI%20investments%20this%20year.%20It's%20not%20100%25%20clear%20how%20that'll%20come%20to%20fruition%2C%20but%20AI%20agents%20will%20likely%20play%20a%20key%20role%2C%20and%20businesses%20are%20starting%20to%20think%20about%20how%20to%20build%20commercial%20models%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUncertainty%20around%20Trump's%20new%20administration%20remains%20a%20business%20risk%2C%20but%20there's%20optimism%20tariffs%20won't%20be%20so%20strong%20they'll%20stop%20businesses%20in%20their%20tracks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20excitement%20around%20the%20return%20of%20the%20M%26amp%3BA%20and%20the%20IPO%20market%20is%20palpable%2C%20as%20exit%20opportunities%20will%20allow%20the%20wider%20business%20lifecycle%20to%20get%20moving%20again.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94%20Dan%20DeFrancesco%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229009f4cb-f3f6-4820-8bdf-a4424ad091b8%5C%22%3EWhat%20it%20really%20takes%20to%20help%20people%20find%20and%20thrive%20in%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20panel%20I%20moderated%20about%20the%20global%20jobs%20gap%2C%20the%20organizers%20told%20me%20%3Cstrong%3Ethe%20president%20of%20Singapore%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20would%20speak%20first%2C%20for%20about%20five%20minutes.%20The%20president%2C%20%3Cstrong%3ETharman%20Shanmugaratnam%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20ended%20up%20speaking%20for%20more%20than%2015%20minutes%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20was%20riveting.%20(You%20can%20watch%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DB_pxV2YG2i4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20soft-spoken%20tone%2C%20reminding%20me%20of%20a%20grandfather%20calmly%20dispensing%20wisdom%2C%20President%20Tharman%20urged%20the%20audience%20to%20think%20broadly%20about%20how%20to%20solve%20the%20mounting%20problems%20of%20global%20un-%20and%20under-employment.%20It's%20not%20just%20about%20wages%20and%20job%20creation%2C%20he%20said.%20It's%20about%20how%20we%20raise%20children%20(the%20first%20three%20years%2C%20he%20said%2C%20are%20critical).%20It's%20about%20how%20we%20educate%20people%20(countries%20with%20strong%20public%20school%20systems%20where%20a%20wide%20swath%20of%20people%20can%20participate%20and%20benefit%20do%20better%2C%20he%20said).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20higher%20education%2C%20it's%20about%20giving%20people%20relevant%20skills%20that%20can%20serve%20them%20and%20not%20leave%20them%20feeling%20dispirited%20that%20their%20investment%20in%20education%20(perhaps%20their%20family's%20or%20the%20state's)%20didn't%20pay%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20argued%20that%20liberal%20arts%20education%20is%20not%20a%20match%20for%20many%20people%20for%20jobs%20and%20that%20the%20so-called%20soft%20skills%20that%20such%20education%20provides%20can%20also%20be%20gained%20in%20more%20technical%20training.%20%26quot%3BSoft%20skills%20are%20not%20the%20sole%20providence%20of%20traditional%20academic%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come%2C%20many%20people%20will%20work%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Binformal%26quot%3B%20sector%20of%20employment%20rather%20than%20full-time%20jobs%20with%20benefits%2C%20and%20it's%20imperative%20that%20people%20in%20those%20jobs%20also%20have%20ways%20to%20develop%20skills%20and%20enjoy%20basic%20protections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClearly%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20it's%20worth%20listening%20for%20yourself.%20As%20the%20workplace%20continues%20to%20evolve%2C%20we%20intend%20to%20be%20your%20place%20to%20help%20you%20navigate%20it.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94%20Jamie%20Heller%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222f3bcae9-8b50-4978-b862-d3385a8f588b%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20better%20way%20to%20Davos%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20most%20Davos-goers%2C%20The%20Promenade%20is%20where%20the%20action%20happens.%20Not%20for%20%3Cstrong%3ECloudflare%20CEO%20Matthew%20Prince%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20this%20year%2C%20who%20told%20us%20he%20spent%20the%20first%20three%20days%20of%20this%20year's%20Davos%20barreling%20down%20the%20nearby%20ski%20slopes%20with%20clients%20and%20some%20members%20of%20the%20US%20ski%20team.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20he's%20confident%20that%20swapping%20the%20meeting%20room%20for%20the%20ski%20lift%20will%20pay%20off.%20%26quot%3BWe'll%20do%20more%20business%20this%20year%20than%20ever%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20Maybe%20that's%20a%20good%20tip%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20us%20for%202026%3F%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94%20Hugh%20Langley%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavos-world-economic-forum-ai-donald-trump-economy-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737719840000%2C%22visual%22