ut's%20new%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Delhi%3A%20MEA%20Spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20also%20seen%20several%20reports%20on%20how%20the%20film%2C%20'Emergency'%2C%20which%20was%20being%20screened%20in%20several%20halls%20was%20being%20obstructed.%20We%20consistently%20raise%20concerns%20with%20the%20UK%20Government%20regarding%20incidents%20of%20violent%20protest%20and%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FUULvcx3QLP%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FUULvcx3QLP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1882741616877936701%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2024%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EBob%20Blackman%2C%20a%20MP%20for%20the%20Conservative%20Party%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20Sunday%2C%20many%20of%20my%20constituents%20gathered%20and%20paid%20for%20a%20screening%20of%20'Emergency'%20in%20the%20Harrow%20Vue%20cinema.%20After%20about%2030%20or%2040%20minutes%2C%20masked%20Khalistani%20terrorists%20burst%20in%2C%20threatened%20audience%20members%20and%20forced%20the%20screening%20to%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20disruptions%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bvery%20controversial%26quot%3B%20film%20were%20reported%20from%20Wolverhampton%2C%20Birmingham%2C%20and%20Manchester%2C%20prompting%20at%20least%20two%20movie%20theatre%20chains%20to%20pull%20the%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20film%20is%20very%20controversial%2C%20and%20I%20am%20not%20commenting%20on%20its%20quality%20or%20content...%20but%20I%20defend%20the%20right%20of%20my%20constituents%2C%20and%20other%20members'%20constituents%2C%20to%20be%20able%20to%20view%20it%20and%20make%20a%20decision%20on%20it.%20It%20covers%20the%20period%20when%20Indira%20Gandhi%20was%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20some%20British%20Sikh%20groups%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Sikh%20Press%20Association%2C%20had%20organised%20protests%20against%20what%20they%20said%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Banti-Sikh%26quot%3B%20movie%2C%20and%20that%20these%20had%20resulted%20in%20disrupted%20shows%20in%20the%20towns%20named%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Ranaut's%20'Emergency'%20faced%20a%20torrid%20time%20getting%20past%20the%20censors%20in%20India%20after%20Sikh%20organisations%20objected%20to%20its%20release.%20They%20accused%20the%20film's%20makers%20-%20Ms%20Ranaut%20is%20one%20of%20the%20producers%20-%20of%20misrepresenting%20the%20Sikh%20community%20and%20twisting%20historical%20facts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Explains%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkangana-ranauts-emergency-stuck-in-massive-row-what-are-the-objections-6487046%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKangana%20Ranaut's%20'Emergency'%20Stuck.%20What%20Are%20The%20Objections%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20these%20concerns%2C%20government%20sources%20acknowledged%20the%20fact%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20some%20sensitive%20content%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20religious%20sentiments%20could%20not%20be%20hurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20back-and-forth%20between%20the%20Censor%20Board%20and%20the%20courts%2C%20the%20film%20was%20cleared%20mid-November%20-%20after%20making%20three%20cuts%20and%20providing%20sources%20for%20certain%20controversial%20dialogues%20-%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Femergency-after-several-delays-kangana-ranauts-film-gets-a-release-date-7045377%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslotted%20for%20a%20January%2017%20release%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong