A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20who%20claims%20that%20he%20is%20a%20true%20disciple%20of%20the%20late%20Karpuri%20Thakur%2C%20has%20been%20a%20staunch%20critic%20of%20dynastic%20politics.%20But%20rumours%20are%20that%20many%20of%20Nitish's%20allies%20would%20like%20Nishant%20to%20be%20made%20his%20political%20%E2%80%98heir'%2C%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20continuity.%20For%20his%20part%2C%20Nishant%20has%2C%20so%20far%2C%20maintained%20a%20low%20profile%20and%20appeared%20to%20have%20evinced%20no%20interest%20in%20things%20political.%20The%20next%20few%20months%20will%20reveal%20the%20younger%20Kumar's%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20in%20the%20Indian%20political%20context%2C%20from%20Kashmir%20to%20Kanyakumari%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20sons%E2%80%94and%20daughters%E2%80%94is%20nothing%20extraordinary.%20Everybody%20who%20is%20anybody%20in%20politics%20has%20promoted%20their%20children%20at%20some%20point.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20its%20first%20family.%20While%20loyalists%20think%20it's%20an%20asset%2C%20the%20detractors%20see%20it%20as%20a%20liability.%20While%20the%20former%20say%20that%20the%20family%20has%20kept%20the%20party%20united%2C%20others%20insist%20that%20it%20has%20made%20the%20organisation%20a%20status%20quo-ist%20grouping%20that%20lacks%20fresh%20blood%20and%20spirit.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFamilies%20In%20The%20South%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20south%2C%20barring%20perhaps%20Kerala%2C%20most%20states%20have%20seen%20families%20shaping%20their%20political%20landscape.%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Udhaynaidhi%20Stalin%20is%20expected%20to%20carry%20forward%20the%20legacy%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20DMK%20supremo%20MK%20Stalin%2C%20who%20himself%20is%20the%20son%20of%20the%20late%20M.%20Karunanidhi.%20Nara%20Lokesh%20is%20a%20rising%20star%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20his%20father%20and%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20supremo%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20is%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20Interestingly%20also%2C%20the%20opposition%20leader%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Y.S.%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%2C%20who%20lost%20power%20last%20year%2C%20is%20the%20son%20of%20the%20late%20Y.S.%20Rajsekhar%20Reddy%2C%20who%20had%20been%20at%20the%20helm%20for%20two%20terms%20in%20the%20state.%20In%20Karnataka%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20(JD-S)%20supremo%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda's%20son%2C%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20the%20current%20Union%20minister%20and%20former%20Karnataka%20chief%20minister%2C%20is%20leading%20the%20party.%20%C2%A0In%20neighbouring%20Telangana%2C%20K.%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20was%20attempting%20a%20hat-trick%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20but%20lost%20badly%20for%20what%20the%20opposition%20dubbed%20his%20%E2%80%98dynastic%20rule'.%20His%20son%2C%20son-in-law%2C%20and%20daughter%20were%20influential%20figures%20in%20his%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbdullahs%20In%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20Yadavs%20In%20UP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20faraway%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20National%20Conference%20supremo%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20facilitated%20the%20swearing-in%20of%20his%2054-year-old%20son%20Omar%20Abdullah%2C%20the%20first%20Chief%20Minister%20to%20take%20the%20reins%20in%20the%20state%20since%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370%20in%202019.%20This%20is%20Omar's%20second%20term%3B%20the%20first%20was%20when%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20used%20to%20be%20a%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Hindi-speaking%20belt%2C%20there%20is%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Hemant%20Soren%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20in%20Rajasthan%E2%80%94all%20products%20of%20dynasty%20and%20family.%20In%20poll-bound%20Bihar%2C%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20patriarch%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20has%20already%20declared%20his%20son%20Tejaswi%20as%20his%20political%20successor%3B%20his%20other%20son%2C%20Tej%20Pratap%2C%20and%20daughter%2C%20Misa%2C%20are%20also%20ambitious%20and%20active%20in%20politics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFamily%20Feuds%20In%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETowards%20the%20West%2C%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20problems%20in%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20arose%20when%20he%20started%20promoting%20his%20daughter%2C%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20and%20ignoring%20his%20nephew%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20split%20in%20Shiv%20Sena%20was%20also%2C%20to%20an%20extent%2C%20due%20to%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20endorsing%20his%20son%20Aditya%20and%20sidelining%20Eknath%20Shinde.%20Notably%2C%20Shinde's%20son%2C%20Shrikant%2C%20who%20is%20an%20MP%20from%20his%20home%20turf%20of%20Thane%20district%2C%20is%20also%20a%20man%20with%20influence%20in%20the%20party.%20Over%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20Raj%20Thackeray%20had%20parted%20ways%20with%20Sena%20because%20his%20uncle%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20patriarch%20Bal%20Thackeray%20chose%20his%20son%2C%20Uddhav%2C%20as%20his%20heir%2C%20ignoring%20the%20firebrand%20nephew.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20state's%20political%20spectrum%2C%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20who%20led%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20the%20state%20to%20a%20record%20win%20in%20Maharashtra%20in%20the%20recent%20assembly%20polls%2C%20is%20also%20somewhat%20a%20product%20of%20dynasty.%20His%20father%2C%20the%20late%20Gangadhar%2C%20was%20an%20MLC%20from%20Nagpur%20decades%20ago.%20Several%20other%20ministers%20in%20his%20government%20have%20risen%20owing%20to%20their%20families%2C%20including%20Nitesh%20Rane%2C%20Radhakrishna%20Vikhe%20Patil%2C%20and%20a%20host%20of%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELegacy%20Questions%20In%20Bengal%20And%20Odisha%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20boss%20and%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20demolished%20the%20Left%20Front%20rule%20in%20the%20state%2C%20seems%20to%20be%20in%20a%20dilemma%20about%20who%20her%20political%20successor%20should%20be.%20Her%20nephew%20and%20MP%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20was%20briefly%20given%20the%20role%2C%20but%20there%20have%20been%20reports%20about%20differences%20between%20them.%20In%20neighbouring%20Odisha%20too%2C%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20chief%20Naveen%20Patnaik%2C%20who%20had%20been%20at%20the%20helm%20for%20over%20two%20decades%20without%20a%20break%2C%20has%20not%20succeeded%20so%20far%20in%20finding%20an%20heir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDynasty%20continues%20to%20influence%20India's%20politics%20heavily.%20Is%20it%20something%20to%20do%20with%20culture%3F%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20doctor's%20son%20becomes%20a%20doctor%20and%20a%20lawyer's%20son%20follows%20him%2C%20what%20is%20wrong%20if%20the%20politician's%20son%20becomes%20a%20politician%20too%3F%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20common%20refrain%2C%20however%20flawed%20it%20may%20be.%20Perhaps%20one%20should%20not%20expect%20things%20to%20change%20too%20much%20in%20the%20near%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sunil%20Gatade%20is%20a%20former%20associate%20editor%20with%20PTI.%20Venkatesh%20Kesari%20was%20an%20assistant%20editor%20with%20The%20Asian%20Age.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737717180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F76262bjo_nishant-kumar_625x300_24_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnishant-kumar-another-son-rises-7548986%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20been%20a%20staunch%20critic%20of%20dynastic%20politics.%20But%20rumours%20are%20that%20many%20of%20Nitish's%20allies%20would%20like%20Nishant%20to%20be%20made%20his%20political%20heir%2C%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20continuity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.n