%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22beadf53d-b9fc-4bef-9f2f-eb3f8b9df2d6%5C%22%3EAn%20immediate%20hit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraitors-creator-marc-pos-dozens-rejections-kept-pitching-until-yes-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20set-up%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Traitors%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20what%20makes%20it%20so%20special.%20It%20hinges%20on%20deceit%20and%20teamwork%20in%20equal%20measure%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20gorgeous%20and%20secluded%20Scottish%20castle.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20loosely%20based%20on%20the%20board%20games%20Mafia%20or%20Werewolf%20and%20first%20appeared%20as%20%26quot%3BDe%20Verraders%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Netherlands%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20contestants%20have%20to%20work%20together%20to%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20the%20challenges%20and%20increase%20the%20prize%20pot.%20The%20majority%20of%20them%2C%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20faithful%2C%26quot%3B%20also%20have%20to%20weed%20out%20any%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20traitors%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20are%20murdering%20them%20off%20one%20by%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20night%2C%20the%20contestants%20gather%20at%20the%20roundtable%20and%20banish%20the%20person%20they%20think%20is%20most%20likely%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20traitors.%20Later%2C%20the%20traitors%20meet%20and%20decide%20who%20their%20next%20victim%20will%20be.%20The%20faithful%20only%20know%20who%20didn't%20make%20it%20when%20they%20don't%20return%20for%20breakfast%20the%20next%20day%2C%20and%20their%20portrait%20is%20unceremoniously%20flung%20onto%20the%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFans%20knew%20the%20UK%20version%20was%20a%20hit%20from%20the%20first%20episode%20on%20November%2029%2C%202022.%20The%20show%20has%20been%20a%20huge%20ratings%20winner%20for%20the%20BBC%2C%20with%20the%20season%20two%20final%20peaking%20at%20almost%20seven%20million%20viewers.%20The%20US%20edition%2C%20while%20it's%20still%20good%2C%20also%20suffers%20from%20wanting%20to%20dramatize%20the%20lightning%20in%20a%20bottle%20the%20show%20already%20achieved%20%E2%80%94%20something%20I%20think%20holds%20it%20back.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESPOILERS%20ahead!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Traitors%20US%20season%20two%20premiere%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b3adbf6c8f0a134f7a25d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlan%20Cumming%20hosts%20the%20US%20version%20of%20The%20Traitors.%3Cp%3EPeacock%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22824a82ca-c844-4131-8722-60b9c39ec395%5C%22%3ETeamwork%20and%20deceit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20show%20is%20presented%20by%20Claudia%20Winkleman%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20players%20through%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20game%20and%20the%20various%20challenges.%20In%20the%20US%20version%2C%20it's%20Alan%20Cumming.%20Both%20are%20excellent%20hosts%20and%20fashionistas%2C%20and%20I%20would%20love%20to%20see%20them%20team%20up%20at%20some%20point%2C%20even%20just%20for%20the%20beautifully%20rustic%20tartan%20outfits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20UK%20%26quot%3BTraitors%26quot%3B%20fills%20the%20castle%20with%20complete%20strangers%2C%20many%20contestants%20on%20the%20US%20version%20have%20already%20appeared%20on%20reality%20TV%20shows%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BBig%20Brother%26quot%3B%20or%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BReal%20Housewives%26quot%3B%20editions.%20Admittedly%2C%20I%20only%20recognized%20Kate%20Chastain%20from%20%26quot%3BBelow%20Deck%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20John%20Bercow%2C%20a%20former%20Speaker%20of%20the%20UK%20House%20of%20Commons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20get%20the%20vision%2C%20but%20immediately%2C%20this%20made%20me%20a%20bit%20wary%20because%20reality%20show%20contestants%20already%20have%20an%20idea%20of%20how%20production%20works.%20They%20know%20how%20to%20get%20screen%20time%20and%20have%20their%20moment%20in%20the%20spotlight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20worry%20was%20that%20in%20the%20US%20version%2C%20both%20the%20audience%20and%20the%20contestants%20have%20pre-judgments%20of%20one%20another.%20You%20also%20missed%20out%20on%20important%20context%20if%20you%20haven't%20seen%20those%20other%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20strangers%20take%20part%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20sets%20the%20audience%20up%20nicely%20for%20getting%20to%20know%20them%20as%20the%20game%20progresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20difference%20was%20the%20players'%20attitudes.%20In%20the%20UK%20version%2C%20there%20was%20a%20big%20emphasis%20on%20teamwork.%20The%20players%20all%20knew%20there%20were%20traitors%20among%20them%2C%20but%20their%20camaraderie%20as%20a%20team%20always%20came%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%20version%2C%20almost%20everyone%20seemed%20to%20have%20a%20secret.%20This%20made%20it%20hard%20for%20the%20players%20to%20trust%20one%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20actually%20a%20fate%20that%20season%203%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20the%20finale%20of%20which%20airs%20on%20Friday%2C%20seems%20to%20be%20suffering%20from.%20The%20show%20depends%20on%20the%20delicate%20balance%20between%20trust%20and%20deceit.%20But%20a%20common%20critique%20this%20year%20is%20that%20the%20contestants%20aren't%20playing%20as%20a%20team%20as%20they%20did%20in%20previous%20seasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20this%20just%20the%20way%20reality%20TV%20goes%20when%20it%20is%20proven%20to%20be%20popular%3F%20Does%20it%20suffer%20from%20its%20notoriety%20and%20then%20attract%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20person%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221944%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harry%20Clark%2C%20The%20Traitors%20season%202%20champion%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6790edcaae09223df2baef37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221296%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20champion%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Traitors%26quot%3B%20UK%20season%202%2C%20Harry%20Clark.%3Cp%3EBBC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22834caf75-2c9b-4229-ab26-553dd3895353%5C%22%3EYou%20need%20to%20root%20for%20someone%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20versions%20of%20the%20show%2C%20there's%20little%20evidence%20to%20go%20on%2C%20so%20the%20faithful%20are%20voted%20out%20at%20an%20alarming%20rate%20at%20the%20beginning.%20But%20in%20the%20US%20version%2C%20they%20would%20be%20weirdly%20candid%20about%20voting%20for%20someone%20else%20simply%20to%20save%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20flaw%20in%20my%20view.%20It%20made%20them%20all%20pretty%20hard%20to%20root%20for.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20I%20sort%20of%20wanted%20Cirie%20to%20win%2C%20but%20I%20also%20didn't%20really%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20seasons%20one%20and%20two%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20Wilf%20and%20Harry%2C%20respectively%2C%20will%20go%20down%20as%20impeccable%20traitors.%20Wilf%20fell%20at%20the%20final%20hurdle%20while%20Harry%20played%20with%20all%20his%20fellow%20contestants%20like%20putty%20until%20the%20very%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20contestants%20also%20just%20seemed%20to%20respect%20the%20game%20more.%20Whenever%20someone%20was%20banished%2C%20they%20would%20leave%20immediately.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20they%20all%20took%20advantage%20of%20their%20reality%20show%20moment%2C%20getting%20in%20the%20last%20word%2C%20swearing%2C%20throwing%20out%20insults%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20players%20also%20got%20up%20to%20say%20goodbye%2C%20which%20just%20felt%20a%20bit%20jarring%20and%20went%20against%20the%20escapism%20aspect.%20Respect%20the%20decorum%20of%20the%20game%20I%20say!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222042%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%26quot%3BThe%20Traitors%26quot%3B%20roundtable%2C%20with%20contestants%20blindfolded.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6790ee132fcded5e9074292d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221526%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EClaudia%20Winkleman%20chooses%20her%20traitors%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Traitors%26quot%3B%20UK%20season%20three.%3Cp%3EBBC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20show%20definitely%20has%20its%20great%20moments.%20In%20season%20one%2C%20when%20the%20players%20voted%20Christian%20out%20after%20his%20chaotic%20gameplay%2C%20it%20was%20very%20satisfying.%20But%20that%20was%20nothing%20compared%20with%20Hannah%2C%20in%20UK%20season%201%2C%20flipping%20the%20script%20on%20her%20best%20friend%20and%20traitor%2C%20Wilf%2C%20right%20at%20the%20last%20second%2C%20throwing%20her%20pouch%20into%20the%20fire%20for%20it%20to%20burn%20red%2C%20revealing%20she%20was%20finally%20seeing%20him%20for%20what%20he%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReality%20stars%20bring%20their%20own%20drama%2C%20but%20no%20amount%20of%20needless%20cliffhangers%20will%20compare%20to%20Miles's%20panicked%20reaction%20that%20Diane%20survived%20his%20murder%20attempt%2C%20or%20indeed%2C%20Ross%20throwing%20out%20a%20wink%20to%20the%20camera%20in%20plain%20sight%20while%20his%20fellow%20faithful%20knew%20nothing%20about%20Diane%20being%20his%20actual%20mother.%20Nothing%2C%20too%2C%20can%20top%20Harry%20ousting%20Paul%20because%20he%20became%20too%20big%20for%20his%20boots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20none%20of%20the%20glorious%20buffoonery%20that%20the%20UK%20is%20known%20for%2C%20like%20Meryl%20winning%20in%20season%201%20completely%20by%20accident%2C%20or%20when%20Ross%20was%20recruited%20as%20a%20traitor%20only%20to%20fail%20spectacularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20it%20all%20just%20felt%20a%20little%20too%20serious%20at%20times.%20When%20Cirie%20took%20all%20the%20money%20for%20herself%20at%20the%20end%20of%20season%201%2C%20it%20was%20bittersweet%20rather%20than%20electrifying%2C%20like%20when%20Harry%20betrayed%20Mollie%20in%20the%20final%20of%20UK%20season%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarry%20was%20correct%20in%20his%20exclamations%20after%20his%20win.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Traitors%26quot%3B%20truly%20is%20the%20best%20game%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20normies%20who%20have%20no%20aspirations%20to%20be%20famous%20are%20an%20important%20part%20of%20that.%20It's%20a%20dramatic%2C%20heartfelt%2C%20tense%2C%20and%20ridiculous%20game%20at%20its%20core%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20there's%20just%20no%20need%20to%20gild%20the%20lily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraitors-us-uk-versions-clear-winner-alan-cumming-peacock-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737714960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678fa0832fcded5e9073f463%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraitors-us-uk-versions-clear-winner-alan-cumming-peacock-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20British%20version%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Traitors%26quot%3B%20outshines%20its%20US%20counterpart%2C%20with%20superior%20gameplay%20dynamics%2C%20production%20styles%2C%20and%20contestant%20attitudes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ldodgson%40businessinsider.com%20(Lindsay%20Dodgson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraitors-us-uk-versions-clear-winner-alan-cumming-peacock-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20declassifies%20JFK%2C%20RFK%2C%20and%20MLK%20files%3A%20Unveiling%20the%20stories%20behind%20their%20assassinations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737714900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117515150%2Cimgsize-891416.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdonald-trump-declassifies-jfk-rfk-and-mlk-files-unveiling-the-stories-behind-their-assassinations%2Farticleshow%2F117513709.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F117513709.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%