ted%20for%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fe3ccc64-7623-4fa5-8277-057e84665613%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20learned%20web%20development%20and%20graphic%20design%20to%20pivot%20to%20a%20new%20career%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20attended%20a%20front-end%20coding%20boot%20camp%20called%20Thinkful%20and%20took%20graphic%20design%20classes%20at%20the%20Academy%20of%20Art%20University%20to%20hone%20a%20new%20skill%20set.%20I%20finally%20shifted%20to%20a%20new%20job%20in%202016%3A%20A%20contract%20position%20at%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recruiter%20reached%20out%20about%20the%20opportunity%2C%20and%20both%20the%20recruiter%20and%20Google's%20hiring%20manager%20were%20impressed%20by%20my%20portfolio.%20My%20teaching%20background%20was%20also%20seen%20as%20an%20asset%20for%20a%20role%20with%20the%20customer%20education%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stepped%20into%20a%20world%20of%20innovation%20and%20speed.%20I%20remember%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20it%2C%20I've%20made%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20I%20soon%20realized%20the%20pace%20at%20Google%20was%20a%20different%20beast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228aec94f3-5181-4652-be02-38e21e51c184%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EStarting%20at%20Google%20was%20a%20rude%20awakening%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20started%2C%20I'd%20seen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdQO3xK9g_CE%26t%3D161s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20resort-like%20experience%20Google%20employees%20had%20every%20day.%20It%20looked%20like%20heaven%2C%20and%20I%20dreamed%20of%20being%20a%20part%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20soon%20learned%20the%20resort-like%20experience%20I'd%20dreamed%20about%20was%20only%20a%20small%20part%20of%20Google%20culture.%20I%20hadn't%20considered%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbreak-into-tech-quit-teaching-coding-boot-camp-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etransitioning%20from%20a