20incident%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blast%20occurred%20in%20the%20LTP%20section%20of%20the%20factory%20around%2010.30%20am%2C%20District%20Collector%20Sanjay%20Kolte%20had%20said%20earlier.%20Firefighters%20and%20medical%20staff%20were%20at%20the%20scene%20to%20contain%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20led%20to%20the%20roof%20collapse%20and%20trapped%20over%20a%20dozen%20workers.%20In%20the%20initial%20efforts%2C%20three%20were%20rescued%20alive%20and%20one%20was%20found%20dead.%20An%20excavator%20was%20used%20to%20remove%20the%20debris%2C%20said%20the%20senior%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blast%20was%20of%20such%20an%20intensity%20that%20it%20was%20heard%20from%205%20km%20away.%20A%20thick%20smoke%20was%20seen%20rising%20from%20the%20factory%20in%20a%20video%20captured%20from%20a%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20previous%20update%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20had%20said%20top%20officials%20were%20at%20the%20blast%20site%20and%20rescue%20teams%20from%20Nagpur%20were%20reaching%20soon.%20Medical%20teams%20were%20also%20ready%20to%20help%20if%20needed%2C%20he%20had%20assured.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737710040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F0o32eqag_maharashtra-bhandara-ordnance-factory-blast-_625x300_24_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-feared-dead-in-massive-explosion-at-ordnance-factory-in-maharashtras-bhandara-7547071%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20massive%20blast%20ripped%20through%20an%20ordnance%20factory%20near%20Nagpur%20this%20morning%2C%20killing%20eight%20workers%20and%20injuring%20seven%20others.%20Union%20Minister%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20confirmed%20the%20deaths%20at%20an%20event%20later%20in%20the%20afternoon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-feared-dead-in-massive-explosion-at-ordnance-factory-in-maharashtras-bhandara-7547071%22%2