r-marketers-creators-tiktok-ban-contingency-plans-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtingency%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20contracts%20that%20dictated%20they%20would%20move%20sponsorships%20to%20other%20apps%20in%20the%20event%20TikTok%20went%20dark.%20Others%20spread%20out%20across%20different%20social%20platforms%2C%20like%20Instagram%2C%20YouTube%2C%20and%20Snapchat%2C%20and%20newcomers%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-app-rednote-memes-tiktok-ban-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERedNote%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20many%20in%20the%20TikTok%20community%2C%20it%20was%20still%20unclear%20what%20would%20happen%20next.%20A%20week%20earlier%2C%20a%20lawyer%20for%20the%20company%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20the%20app%20would%20%26quot%3Bgo%20dark%26quot%3B%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-says-wouid-go-dark-january-without-us-court-intervention-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eessentially%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bstop%20operating%26quot%3B%20on%20January%2019%20without%20legal%20or%20political%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Chew%20finally%20emerged%20with%20a%20TikTok%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40tiktok%2Fvideo%2F7460937381265411370%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emessage%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%2012%3A30%20p.m.%20on%20Friday%2C%20he%20didn't%20say%20what%20would%20happen%20over%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20TikTok%20had%20been%20fighting%20to%20%26quot%3Bprotect%20the%20constitutional%20right%20to%20free%20speech%26quot%3B%20for%20Americans%20who%20use%20the%20app.%20%26quot%3BOn%20behalf%20of%20everyone%20at%20TikTok%20and%20all%20our%20users%20across%20the%20country%2C%20I%20want%20to%20thank%20President%20Trump%20for%20his%20commitment%20to%20work%20with%20us%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20that%20keeps%20TikTok%20available%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20flooded%20the%20comments%20section%20of%20Chew's%20video.%20One%20pleaded%20with%20Chew%20not%20to%20sell%20the%20app%3A%20%26quot%3B%5BI%5Dt%20won't%20be%20the%20same.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTikTok%20has%20gotten%20me%20through%20some%20of%20my%20darkest%20moments%20in%20the%20past%205%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20commented.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20eternally%20grateful%20for%20my%20time%20here%20and%20will%20miss%20it%20%F0%9F%92%94%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hours%20after%20the%20ruling%20dropped%2C%20some%20staff%20told%20BI%20they%20felt%20unclear%20about%20what%20would%20happen%20next.%20The%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-tells-staff-still-have-jobs-if-ban-happens-memo-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20US%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20few%20days%20earlier%20that%20their%20employment%2C%20pay%2C%20and%20benefits%20were%20secure%2C%20and%20offices%20would%20remain%20open%20even%20if%20the%20situation%20wasn't%20resolved%20before%20the%20January%2019%20deadline.%20The%20company%20sent%20a%20message%20on%20Friday%20that%20linked%20to%20Chew's%20video%20and%20included%20some%20assurances%20about%20their%20employment%2C%20an%20employee%20said.%20(A%20TikTok%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20company%20communicated%20regularly%20with%20employees%20throughout%20the%20weekend.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20TikTok%20employee%20felt%20there%20was%20no%20work%20to%20be%20done%20that%20day%20with%20the%20app's%20future%20hanging%20in%20the%20balance.%20(The%20staffers%20asked%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20because%20they%20were%20not%20authorized%20to%20speak%20about%20their%20employer.%20Their%20identities%20are%20known%20to%20Business%20Insider.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%208%3A36%20p.m.%20ET%2C%20the%20company%20issued%20a%20written%20statement%20about%20its%20plans%20%E2%80%94%20and%20said%20much%20of%20the%20uncertainty%20lay%20with%20the%20Biden%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnless%20the%20Biden%20Administration%20immediately%20provides%20a%20definitive%20statement%20to%20satisfy%20the%20most%20critical%20service%20providers%20assuring%20non-enforcement%2C%20unfortunately%20TikTok%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20go%20dark%20on%20January%2019%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ca3d1c44-0fc5-409e-907f-99fc27508d85%5C%22%3ESaturday%20afternoon%3A%20Confusion%20swirls%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20TikTok's%20global%20e-commerce%20team%20sent%20out%20an%20%26quot%3Bimportant%20notice%26quot%3B%20to%20its%20Shop%20agency%20partners%2C%20a%20group%20of%20vendors%20that%20work%20with%20merchants%20to%20sell%20products%20on%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20would%20be%20suspended%20at%208%3A30%20p.m.%20ET%2C%20according%20to%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20memo%20reviewed%20by%20BI%2C%20though%20agencies%20could%20continue%20to%20check%20orders%20and%20access%20other%20platform%20data.%20Some%20e-commerce%20partners%20who%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-sellers-brace-for-doomsday-as-us-ban-approaches-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espent%20weeks%20preparing%20for%20a%20potential%20app%20shutdown%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20with%20what%20they%20said%20was%20little%20guidance%20from%20TikTok%20%E2%80%94%20began%20chattering%20about%20the%20app's%20imminent%20demise%2C%20one%20Shop%20partner%20told%20BI.%20(They%20asked%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20to%20protect%20business%20relationships.%20Their%20identity%20is%20known%20to%20BI.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20memo%20appeared%20to%20be%20inaccurate.%20A%20few%20hours%20later%2C%20in%20a%20follow-up%20email%2C%20the%20company%20informed%20its%20partners%20that%20%26quot%3Ban%20unauthorized%20individual%20sent%20an%20erroneous%20email%20about%20TikTok%20Shop's%20business%20service%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20would%20share%20%26quot%3Bofficial%20company%20communications%20with%20users%2C%20creators%2C%20and%20partners%20when%20plans%20are%20finalized.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20idea%20what%20is%20going%20on%20honestly%20lol%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Shop%20partner%20messaged%20BI%20after%20the%20second%20email%20went%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22453085b0-9aa2-43d3-b39a-e9464e82a92d%5C%22%3ESaturday%20around%2010%3A30%20p.m.%20ET%3A%20'Sorry%2C%20TikTok%20isn't%20available%20right%20now'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%20night%2C%20users%20were%20greeted%20with%20a%20pop-up%20when%20they%20opened%20the%20app%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20regret%20that%20a%20U.S.%20law%20banning%20TikTok%20will%20take%20effect%20on%20January%2019%20and%20force%20us%20to%20make%20our%20services%20temporarily%20unavailable.%20We're%20working%20to%20restore%20our%20service%20in%20the%20U.S.%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%20and%20we%20appreciate%20your%20support.%20Please%20stay%20tuned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelirious%20is%20one%20way%20to%20describe%20the%20app's%20final%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20OK%2C%26quot%3B%20Alix%20Earle%20told%20her%207.2%20million%20followers%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20from%20bed%20before%20the%20shutdown%2C%20wiping%20tears%20from%20her%20eyes.%20%26quot%3BSomeone's%20gonna%20have%20to%2C%20like%2C%20check%20me%20into%20a%20mental%20hospital.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarber%20said%20he%20was%20struck%20with%20a%20feeling%20of%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20am%20I%20supposed%20to%20do%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20scrolling%20through%20TikTok%20and%20you're%20seeing%20everybody%20saying%20their%20goodbyes%20in%20tears%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-creators-regret-revealing-secrets-before-trump-reversed-ban-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econfessed%3C%2Fa%3E%20their%20secrets%20to%20millions%20on%20the%20app%2C%20while%20some%20took%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-ban-sparks-humorous-memes-by-users-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomedy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20want%20to%20laugh%20up%20until%20the%20last%20second%20and%20I%20want%20to%20laugh%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Victoria%20Paris%2C%20a%20lifestyle%20content%20creator%20who%20has%20about%202%20million%20followers.%20(Her%20content%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20ban%20included%20several%20videos%20in%20which%20she%20licked%20Jawbreaker%20candy.)%20%26quot%3BI've%20cried%20a%20million%20times%20on%20this%20app.%20You%20don't%20need%20to%20go%20out%20watching%20me%20cry.%20Let's%20go%20out%20watching%20some%20stupid%20shit.%20That's%20why%20we%20love%20this%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20around%2010%3A30%20p.m.%20ET%2C%20TikTok%20called%20it%20quits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSorry%2C%20TikTok%20isn't%20available%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20second%20pop-up%20read.%20%26quot%3BA%20law%20banning%20TikTok%20has%20been%20enacted%20in%20the%20U.S.%20Unfortunately%2C%20that%20means%20you%20can't%20use%20TikTok%20for%20now.%20We%20are%20fortunate%20that%20President%20Trump%20has%20indicated%20that%20he%20will%20work%20with%20us%20on%20a%20solution%20to%20reinstate%20TikTok%20once%20he%20takes%20office.%20Please%20stay%20tuned!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParis%20described%20the%20cutoff%20as%20%26quot%3Bshocking%20and%20jarring.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELukas%20Battle%2C%20a%20comedy%20creator%20with%20around%20620%2C000%20followers%2C%20said%20his%20feed%20was%20frozen%20on%20a%20video%20of%20Jane%20Goodall.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20time%20I%20accidentally%20opened%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20would%20just%20be%20Jane%20Goodall%20and%20a%20piece%20of%20glass%20and%20a%20gorilla%2C%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20I%20love%20this.%20I%20kind%20of%20feel%20like%20this%20is%20a%20good%20representation%20of%20what's%20going%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMinutes%20before%20I%20was%20going%20to%20post%20my%20goodbye%20video%2C%20I%20couldn't%2C%20the%20app%20wouldn't%20let%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Barber%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2207e41ac1-9fe7-4120-8f47-12ee5cb09b07%5C%22%3ESunday%3A%20TikTok's%20game%20of%20chicken%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20about%2014%20hours%2C%20TikTok%20was%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20around%2012%3A30%20p.m.%20ET%2C%20it%20rose%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20agreement%20with%20our%20service%20providers%2C%20TikTok%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20restoring%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20TikTok%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20referring%20to%20partners%20like%20Oracle%20that%20it%20works%20with%20to%20store%20data%20and%20deliver%20videos.%20The%20company%20thanked%20Trump%2C%20whose%20inauguration%20was%20set%20to%20begin%20roughly%2024%20hours%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20that%20morning%2C%20Trump%20posted%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2Fposts%2F113855616848696050%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bissue%20an%20executive%20order%20on%20Monday%20to%20extend%20the%20period%20of%20time%20before%20the%20law's%20prohibitions%20take%20effect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20feeling%20for%20users%20and%20creators%20was%3A%20%3Cem%3EWelp%2C%20that%20was%20a%20waste%20of%20energy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20it%20was%20going%20to%20be%20at%20least%20a%20full%20day%2C%20or%20even%20a%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20Battle%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20have%20whiplash%20from%20it%20coming%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Paris%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvertisers%20received%20an%20email%20from%20TikTok%20on%20Sunday%20that%20reaffirmed%20the%20app%20was%20coming%20back%20to%20a%20majority%20of%20US%20users%20and%20ad%20campaigns%20would%20resume%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20day.%20The%20email%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20was%20reviewed%20by%20BI%2C%20also%20noted%20there%20may%20be%20some%20%26quot%3Btemporary%20service%20instability%26quot%3B%20as%20things%20came%20back%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHours%20later%2C%20TikTok%20was%20sponsoring%20the%20glitzy%20MAGA%20crowd%20in%20the%20nation's%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20saved%20TikTok%2C%26quot%3B%20CJ%20Pearson%2C%20a%20cochair%20of%20the%20Republican%20National%20Committee%20Youth%20Advisory%20Council%2C%20who%20helped%20organize%20the%20party%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DidmV9WzBsE8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20celebrate%20tonight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bba1a9a6-beb9-40d0-9707-81a59f2d542d%5C%22%3EMonday%20and%20beyond%3A%20What's%20next%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%20morning%2C%20Chew%20attended%20the%20inaugural%20festivities%20along%20with%20fellow%20tech%20executives%20including%20Jeff%20Bezos%2C%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20and%20Mark%20Zuckerberg.%20He%20sat%20on%20the%20dais%20next%20to%20Tulsi%20Gabbard%2C%20Trump's%20nominee%20to%20be%20the%20next%20director%20of%20national%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20night%2C%20around%208%20p.m.%20ET%2C%20Trump%20dropped%20a%20new%20executive%20order%20instructing%20his%20future%20attorney%20general%20to%20delay%20enforcing%20the%20TikTok%20ban%20for%2075%20days.%20It%20was%20a%20sharp%20departure%20from%20his%20first%20term%2C%20when%20he%20signed%20an%20August%202020%20executive%20order%20attempting%20to%20force%20TikTok%20out%20of%20app%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Trump%20said%20he%20was%20concerned%20that%20TikTok%20could%20become%20a%20disinformation%20tool%20for%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party.%20He%20also%20feared%20that%20US%20user%20data%20could%20end%20up%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Chinese%20government.%20Members%20of%20Congress%20raised%20similar%20concerns%20when%20they%20passed%20the%202024%20divest-or-ban%20law.%20(TikTok%20has%20previously%20said%20that%20it%20does%20not%20share%20information%20with%20the%20Chinese%20government%20and%20that%20a%20US-based%20team%20operates%20its%20content-moderation%20work%20%26quot%3Bindependently%20from%20China.%26quot%3B)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20few%20weeks%20will%20be%20critical%20for%20TikTok%20and%20ByteDance%20as%20they%20fight%20for%20a%20deal%20that%20keeps%20the%20US%20and%20China%20happy%20%E2%80%94%20without%20destroying%20their%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-tiktok-ban-us-should-own-half-of-tiktok-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproposed%20a%20joint%20venture%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20give%20a%20US%20entity%2050%25%20ownership%20in%20the%20company.%20Various%20potential%20bidders%20have%20also%20emerged%2C%20including%20the%20AI%20startup%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperplexity-bid-to-buy-tiktok-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPerplexity%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20former%20Los%20Angeles%20Dodgers%20owner%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-shark-tank-star-kevin-oleary-bid-frank-mccourt-bytedance-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFrank%20McCourt%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20YouTube%20creator%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fmrbeast-joins-new-bid-to-buy-tiktok-bloomberg-reports-1034254679%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMrBeast%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBill%20Ford%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20General%20Atlantic%2C%20a%20ByteDance%20investor%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2025%2F01%2F22%2Fbytedance-tiktok-ban-deal-china-us-davos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAxios%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20deal%20would%20get%20done%20that's%20%26quot%3Bin%20everybody's%20interest%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20may%20be%20%26quot%3Bshort%20of%20divestiture.%26quot%3B%20But%20if%20the%20whirlwind%20weekend%20is%20any%20in