0and%20the%20AI%20agenda%2C%20in%20my%20mind%2C%20go%20hand%20in%20hand%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Premji%2C%20who%20joined%20Wipro%20in%202007%20and%20worked%20in%20several%20roles%20before%20becoming%20Executive%20Chairman%20in%202019%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWipro%20And%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Premji%20said%20they%20have%20made%20AI%20%26quot%3Ball-pervasive%20inside%20of%20Wipro.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20advent%20of%20any%20technology%20creates%20opportunity%2C%20right%3F%20Because%20the%20technology%20in%20itself%20has%20limited%20bearing.%20The%20value%20of%20the%20technology%20is%20if%20you're%20able%20to%20put%20it%20to%20use%20in%20solving%20specific%20business%20problems%2C%20right%3F%20We've%20done%20a%20couple%20of%20things%20as%20a%20company%20over%20the%20last%20year.%20One%20is%20we've%20made%20AI%20all-pervasive%20inside%20of%20Wipro%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Premji%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20they%20did%20it%20by%20making%202.35%20lakh%20employees%20go%20through%20%26quot%3Bgenerative%20AI%20training%20101%26quot%3B%20starting%20with%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20about%2050%2C000%20people%20who've%20gone%20through%20higher%20levels%20of%20skilling%20and%20certification%20on%20generative%20AI%2C%205%2C000%20people%20at%20the%20next%20level%2C%20500%20people%20at%20the%20highest%20level%20in%20the%20organisation.%20So%20we're%20driving%20it%20all-pervasively%20within%20the%20company%20to%20drive%20a%20very%20strong%20AI%20mindset%2C%20skill%20set%2C%20and%20tool%20set%20inside%20of%20the%20organisation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Fkfb9iiuo_wipro-generic-getty_625x300_12_January_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThree%20Things%20About%20AI%20In%20Wipro%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Premji%20said%20the%20company%20is%20focussing%20on%20three%20things%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%2C%20how%20do%20we%20operate%20better%20as%20a%20company%3F%20How%20do%20we%20leverage%20this%20technology%20(AI)%20to%20disrupt%20ourselves%3F%20And%20we've%20implemented%20this%20in%20all%20of%20our%20functions%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20HR%2C%20finance%2C%20legal%2C%20sales%2C%20skilling%2C%20recruitment%2C%20etc.%20I'll%20give%20you%20a%20very%20simple%20example.%20We%20sign%20400-page%20master%20service%20agreements%20with%20our%20customers.%20We%20sign%20up%20for%20specific%20delivery%20commitments.%20We%20sign%20up%20for%20certain%20timelines.%20We%20sign%20up%20for%20fines%20when%20we%20don't%20deliver%20it.%20How%20many%20of%20our%20delivery%20managers%20are%20reading%20400-page%20documents%3F%20It's%20unreasonable%20to%20expect%20them%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20sponsored%20by%20our%20chief%20legal%20officer%2C%20we're%20driving%20this%20now.%20We're%20leveraging%20the%20technology%20to%20actually%20distill%20that%20down%20into%20a%20few%20pages%20which%20can%20be%20consumable%20and%20very%20clearly%20actionable.%20So%20there%20is%20a%20real%20strong%20application%20of%20the%20technology%20in%20functions%20across%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo%20is%20how%20do%20we%20deliver%20better%3F%20How%20do%20we%20do%20the%20work%20that%20we're%20doing%20inside%20of%20the%20organization%20more%20impactfully%2C%20faster%2C%20more%20autonomously%2C%20etc%3F%20And%20that's%20a%20big%20focus.%20And%20we're%20seeing%20a%20lot%20of%20impact%20on%20that%2C%20specifically%20fixed%20price%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20the%20last%20is%20how%20do%20we%20change%20the%20game%3F%20So%20how%20do%20we%20come%20up%20with%20very%20context-specific%2C%20domain-specific%20use%20cases%20for%20customers%3F%20Operate%20better%2C%20manage%20better%2C%20deliver%20better%2C%20and%20change%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Premji%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20one%20thing%20that's%20becoming%20more%20and%20more%20exciting%20is%20agentic%20AI%2C%20a%20probabilistic%20technology%20with%20high%20adaptability%20to%20changing%20environments%20and%20events.%20The%20advantage%20of%20agentic%20AI%20is%20it's%20autonomous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20highly%20specialised.%20It%20can%20self-heal%20and%20self-learn.%20And%20it%20can%20call%20through%20APIs%20on%20other%20agents%2C%20other%20AI%20agents%2C%20as%20well%20as%20on%20humans..%20The%20technology%20exists.%20The%20ability%20of%20leveraging%20it%20to%20solve%20business-case%20problems%2C%20real-life%20problems%2C%20is%20where%20the%20magic%20is...%20There%20is%20no%20AI%20without%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20challenge%20with%20most%20large%20enterprises%20is%20they're%20complex.%20They're%20messy%20at%20times.%20They%20don't%20have%20modernised%20applications.%20They%20don't%20have%20data%20that's%20well-structured%2C%20well-architected.%20How%20do%20they%20leverage%20it%20completely%20to%20get%20the%20benefits%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20are%20things%20that%20customers%20are%20very%20much%20focused%20on.%20And%20so%20the%20opportunity%20to%20serve%20customers%20from%20a%20tech%20services%20perspective...%20I%20think%20it%20presents%20a%20tremendous%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Premji%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20on%20the%20boards%20of%20Wipro%20Enterprises%20Limited%2C%20a%20leading%20player%20in%20FMCG%20and%20infrastructure%20engineering%3B%20Wipro-GE%2C%20a%20joint%20healthcare%20venture%20between%20Wipro%20and%20General%20Electric%2C%20and%20the%20Azim%20Premji%20Foundation%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20not-for-profit%20initiatives%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five-day%20meeting%20at%20Davos%20that%20began%20on%20Monday%20explored%20how%20to%20