%20proposed%20changes%20to%2044%20sections%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fwaqf-act%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWaqf%20Act%20of%201955%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspensions%20followed%20ruckus%20in%20the%20JPC%20hearing%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20day's%20meeting%20began%20on%20a%20stormy%20note%3B%20opposition%20MPs%20shouted%20down%20proceedings%2C%20saying%20they%20were%20not%20being%20given%20enough%20time%20to%20study%20the%20changes%20suggested%20to%20the%20Waqf%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20before%20the%20JPC%20was%20to%20hear%20from%20Mirwaiz%20Umar%20Farooq%2C%20Kashmir's%20religious%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20was%20delayed%20after%20opposition%20MPs%20accused%20others%20on%20the%20committee%20-%20specifically%20those%20from%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20-%20of%20rushing%20the%20bill%20through%20in%20time%20for%20next%20month's%20Delhi%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heated%20arguments%20that%20followed%20forced%20brief%20adjournment%2C%20and%20the%20delegation%20led%20by%20the%20Mirwaiz%20appeared%20after%20the%20committee%20reconvened.%20But%20the%20peace%20didn't%20last%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Banerjee%20and%20the%20Congress'%20Naseer%20Hussain%20then%20stormed%20out%2C%20complaining%20the%20committee%20and%20its%20proceedings%20had%20become%20a%20%26quot%3Bfarce%26quot%3B.%20The%20BJP's%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20called%20their%20conduct%20%26quot%3Bagainst%20Parliamentary%20practice%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20suppress%20the%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20them%2C%20as%20the%20hearing%20continued%2C%20the%20Mirwaiz%20told%20the%20committee%20he%20could%20not%20support%20the%20proposed%20changes%20to%20the%20Waqf%20laws%20as%20they%20meant%20the%20government%20was%20interfering%20in%20religious%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20our%20suggestions%20will%20be%20heard%20and%20(be)%20acted%20upon%2C%20and%20no%20such%20step%20will%20be%20taken%20that%20could%20make%20Muslims%20feel%20like%20they%20are%20being%20disempowered%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20issue%20of%20Waqf%20is%20a%20very%20serious%20matter%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20as%20it%20is%20a%20Muslim-majority%20state.%20Many%20people%20have%20concerns%20regarding%20this%20(and)%20we%20want%20the%20government%20to%20refrain%20from%20interfering%20in%20Waqf%20matters%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeetings%20of%20this%20committee%20have%20seen%20mud-slinging%20and%20even%20physical%20brawls%20since%20it%20was%20set%20up%20in%20August%20last%20year%3B%20in%20October%2C%20for%20example%2C%20Mr%20Banerjee%20had%20a%20'Hulk'%20moment%2C%20smashing%20a%20glass%20bottle%20on%20the%20table%20and%20throwing%20it%20at%20the%20BJP's%20Jagadambika%20Pal%2C%20the%20committee%20Chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-joint-parliamentary-committee-kalyan-banerjee-trinamools-kalyan-banerjee-explains-hulk-moment-during-waqf-bill-meeting-6899719%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrinamool%20MP%20Explains%20'Hulk'%20Moment%20During%20Waqf%20Bill%20Meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20explained%20his%20actions%2C%20saying%20another%20BJP%20MP%2C%20ex-Calcutta%20High%20Court%20judge%20Abhijit%20Gangopadhyay%20flung%20verbal%20abuses%20at%20his%20family%20and%20provoked%20that%20strong%20reaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20proposes%20numerous%20changes%20to%20the%20way%20Waqf%20boards%20are%20administered%2C%20including%20nominating%20non-Muslim%20and%20(at%20least%20two)%20women%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Explains%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-act-amendment-explainer-women-non-muslims-on-boards-council-cant-claim-land-waqf-act-changes-6282656%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWomen%2C%20Non-Muslims%2C%20Council%20Can't%20Claim%20Land%3A%20Waqf%20Changes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20central%20Waqf%20Council%20must%20(if%20the%20amendments%20are%20passed)%20include%20a%20union%20minister%20and%20three%20MPs%2C%20as%20also%20two%20ex-judges%2C%20four%20people%20of%20'national%20repute'%2C%20and%20senior%20government%20officials%2C%20none%20of%20whom%20need%20be%20from%20the%20Islamic%20faith.%20Further%2C%20the%20Council%20can't%20claim%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20proposed%20changes%20are%20to%20limit%20donations%20from%20Muslims%20who%20have%20been%20practicing%20their%20faith%20for%20at%20least%20five%20years%20(a%20provision%20that%20triggered%20a%20row%20over%20the%20term%20'practicing%20Muslim'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20NDTV%20the%20idea%20is%20to%20empower%20Muslim%20women%20and%20children%20who%20%26quot%3Bsuffered%26quot%3B%20under%20the%20old%20law.%20However%2C%20critics%20of%20the%20proposed%20changes%2C%20including%20opposition%20leaders%20like%20the%20Congress'%20KC%20Venugopal%2C%20have%20said%20it%20constitutes%20a%20%26quot%3Bdirect%20attack%20on%20freedom%20of%20religion%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-parliament-6291509%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpposition%20Targets%20Non-Muslims%20Provision%20In%20%26quot%3BDraconian%26quot%3B%20Waqf%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Owaisi%20and%20the%20DMK's%20Kanimozhi%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20have%20argued%20it%20violates%20multiple%20sections%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20including%20Article%2015%20(the%20right%20to%20practice%20a%20religion%20of%20one's%20choice)%20and%20Article%2030%20(the%20right%20to%20minority%20communities%20to%20establish%20and%20administer%20their%20educational%20institutions).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ET