to%20kill%20Kejriwal'%3A%20AAP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737705204000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117513742%2Cimgsize-810720.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Faap-lodges-complaint-with-ec-over-alleged-attacks-on-arvind-kejriwal-during-poll-campaign%2Farticleshow%2F117513475.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AAP%20has%20accused%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20and%20Delhi%20Police%20of%20conspiring%20to%20kill%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20The%20party%20has%20requested%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20to%20reinstate%20Kejriwal's%20security%20cover%2C%20alleging%20repeated%20attacks%20during%20his%20campaigns.%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%20chief%20ministers%20claimed%20these%20threats%20were%20orchestrated%20under%20the%20directives%20of%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Faap-lodges-complaint-with-ec-over-alleged-attacks-on-arvind-kejriwal-during-poll-campaign%2Farticleshow%2F117513475.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22FIITJEE%20Centers%20Shut%20Across%20UP%2C%20Delhi%20As%20Teachers%20Quit%20Over%20Unpaid%20Salaries%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20eight%20FIITJEE%20(Forum%20For%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology-Joint%20Entrance%20Examination)%20coaching%20centres%20across%20North%20India%20have%20abruptly%20shut%20over%20the%20past%20week%2C%20leaving%20hundreds%20of%20students%20and%20parents%20fuming%20ahead%20of%20board%20and%20entrance%20examinations.%20The%20closure%20came%20after%20several%20teachers%20at%20the%20institute%20quit%20en%20masse%20due%20to%20unpaid%20salaries%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIITJEE%20coaching%20centres%20in%20Noida%2C%20Ghaziabad%2C%20Bhopal%2C%20Varanasi%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Patna%20have%20shut%20down.%20A%20centre%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Meerut%20was%20the%20latest%20to%20close%20recently.%20According%20to%20officials%2C%20the%20centre's%20administration%20initially%20tried%20to%20arrange%20for%20teachers%20from%20Noida%2C%20but%20that%20lasted%20only%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20days.%20Following%20this%2C%20they%20had%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20parents%20have%20filed%20police%20complaints%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20private%20coaching%20institution%20did%20not%20give%20them%20any%20notice%20or%20their%20refunds.%20Several%20pictures%20and%20videos%20showed%20the%20parents%20protesting%20outside%20the%20institute's%20now-shut%20branches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeveral%20FIITJEE%20coaching%20institutes%20were%20shut%20around%20six%20months%20ago%20in%20some%20states...After%20that%2C%20they%20told%20us%20that%20these%20centres%20would%20not%20shut%20down%20and%20that%20we%20should%20make%20the%20payments.%20I%20have%20invested%20Rs%206%20lakh%20already...they%20took%20everyone's%20money%20and%20told%20us%20that%20classes%20would%20go%20on.%20Even%20when%20the%20teachers%20left%2C%20they%20said%20we%20would%20still%20manage%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20parent%20of%20a%20student%20studying%20at%20the%20FIITJEE%20institute%20in%20Meerut%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemanding%20a%20solution%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20students'%20moral%20support%20has%20become%20weak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20parent%20who%20had%20recently%20deposited%20a%20Rs%204%20lakh%20fee%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAn%20outgoing%20FIITJEE%20teacher%20told%20us%20that%20most%20faculty%20members%20are%20leaving%20as%20they%20have%20not%20been%20paid%20salaries%20for%20several%20months.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFIITJEE%20has%20been%20going%20through%20a%20crisis%20amid%20speculation%20over%20the%20institute's%20financial%20crisis%20and%20troubles%20due%20to%20fresh%20administrative%20and%20civic%20action%20against%20its%20branches%20for%20violating%2