l%20classes%20were%20forced%20to%20go%20online.%20Everyone%20thought%20this%20would%20change%20education%20in%20India%20forever%2C%20breaking%20down%20barriers%20and%20making%20quality%20learning%20accessible%20at%20a%20click%20for%20everyone.%20Professors%20recorded%20their%20lessons%20and%20students%20began%20learning%20at%20their%20convenience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20what%20once%20was%20flourishing%2C%20began%20collapsing%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinancial%20crisis%2C%20lower%20input%20costs%2C%20and%20cases%20of%20illegal%20registrations%20have%20been%20some%20of%20the%20factors%20responsible%20for%20the%20downfall%20of%20the%20edtech%20system%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20online%20edtech%20not%20booming%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20years%20of%20online%20education%2C%20many%20parents%20are%20sending%20their%20children%20back%20to%20offline%20classes.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20this%20is%20mainly%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20motivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstitutes%20like%20Coursera%2C%20Udemy%2C%20and%20Byjus%20offer%20online%20courses%20wherein%20teachers%20record%20their%20lectures%20or%20set%20a%20time%20for%20live%20discussions%20and%20students%20join%20in.%20But%20a%20report%20by%20Udemy%20claimed%20that%20most%20students%20complete%20just%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20content%20and%20leave.%20Some%20even%20pay%20for%20the%20course%2C%20but%20never%20start%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Byjus%20which%20offers%20online%20learning%20programs%2C%20has%20been%20facing%20a%20severe%20funding%20crunch.%20It%20became%20popular%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20and%20its%20valuation%20shot%20up%20to%20%2422%20billion%20in%202022.%20But%20since%20then%2C%20it%20has%20faced%20demands%20for%20unpaid%20dues%20and%20allegations%20of%20mismanagement.%20It%20also%20allegedly%20entered%20into%20insolvency%20after%20US%20lenders%20complained%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20last%20year%20about%2