move%20celebrated%20by%20the%20Afghan%20Women's%20Movement%20for%20Justice%20and%20Awareness%20as%20a%20step%20towards%20accountability.%20Since%20regaining%20control%20in%202021%2C%20the%20Taliban%20have%20restricted%20women's%20access%20to%20jobs%2C%20public%20spaces%2C%20and%20education%20beyond%20sixth%20grade.%20The%20UN%20described%20the%20ban%20on%20girls%E2%80%99%20education%20as%20a%20tragedy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fafghan-womens-group-hails-courts-move-to-arrest-taliban-leaders-for-persecution-of-women%2Farticleshow%2F117511017.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fafghan-womens-group-hails-courts-move-to-arrest-taliban-leaders-for-persecution-of-women%2Famp_articleshow%2F117511017.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fafghan-womens-group-hails-courts-move-to-arrest-taliban-leaders-for-persecution-of-women%2Famp_articleshow%2F117511017.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Are%20Actor%20Vijay%2C%20AIADMK%20And%20BJP%20Teaming%20Up%20To%20Take%20On%20Stalin%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActor%20Joseph%20Vijay's%20Tamizhaga%20Vetri%20Kazhagam%20(TVK)%20has%20from%20the%20outset%20positioned%20itself%20as%20an%20anti-DMK%20(Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam)%20force%2C%20open%20to%20alliances%20with%20other%20political%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20principal%20opposition%20party%2C%20the%20AIADMK%20(All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam).%20Vijay's%20colleagues%20from%20Tamil%20cinema%20who%20entered%20politics%E2%80%94such%20as%20Kamal%20Haasan%20in%202018%20and%20the%20late%20Vijayakanth%20in%202006%E2%80%94learned%20the%20hard%20way%20that%20it's%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20win%20an%20election%20without%20aligning%20with%20one%20of%20the%20two%20major%20Dravidian%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20actor%20Vijayakanth's%20DMDK%20(Desiya%20Murpokku%20Dravida%20Kazhagam)%20in%20the%202006%20assembly%20election%20and%20Kamal%20Haasan's%20Makkal%20Needhi%20Maiam%20(MNM)%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20both%20positioned%20themselves%20as%20third-force%20alternatives%20to%20both%20the%20DMK%20and%20AIADMK%2C%20but%20neither%20made%20any%20significant%20impact.%20Vijayakanth's%20DMDK%20secured%208%25%20of%20the%20vote%20in%202006%20but%20won%20just%20one%20assembly%20seat.%20But%20in%202011%2C%20when%20he%20joined%20the%20AIADMK%20alliance%2C%20his%20party%20bagged%2028%20seats.%20More%20recently%2C%20Kamal%20Haasan's%20MNM%20saw%20disappointing%20performances%20in%20the%202019%20and%202021%20elections%2C%20leading%20the%20party%20to%20align%20with%20the%20DMK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Two%20Biggest%20Parties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20the%20AIADMK%20and%20the%20DMK%20have%20held%20the%20first%20and%20second-largest%20vote%20shares%20in%20the%20state%2C%20respectively%2C%20even%20during%20their%20worst%20performances.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20DMK's%20worst%20election%20in%20recent%20history%20was%20in%202014%2C%20but%20the%20party%20still%20garnered%2022%25%20of%20the%20votes.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20AIADMK's%20worst%20elections%20in%201996%20and%202004%20saw%20the%20party%20winning%2026%25%20and%2030%25%20votes%2C%20respectively.%20Third%20parties%20have%20never%20surpassed%20single-digit%20vote%20shares%20at%20their%20peak%2C%20underscoring%20the%20necessity%20of%20an%20alliance%20with%20either%20the%20AIADMK%20or%20the%20DMK%20for%20any%20serious%20political%20success.%20This%20reality%20explains%20why%20in%20October%20Vijay%20mentioned%20the%20possibility%20of%20power-sharing%20in%20a%20coalition%20government.%20However%2C%20three%20months%20later%2C%20have%20Vijay%20and%20the%20AIADMK%20moved%20closer%20to%20forming%20an%20alliance%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%2C%20two%20major%20issues%20in%20the%20state%20have%20pointed%20to%20a%20potential%20coordination%20between%20the%20AIADMK%2C%20the%20TVK%2C%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20opposing%20the%20DMK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20the%20Anna%20Varsity%20sexual%20assault%20case%20sparked%20a%20series%20of%20protests%20by%20opposition%20parties%2C%20with%20Vijay%20meeting%20the%20Governor%2C%20who%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20ideological%20ally%20of%20the%20right%20wing%20and%20someone%20antagonistic%20towards%20the%20DMK.%20This%20visit%20was%20timed%20with%20mass%20protests%20organised%20by%20the%20AIADMK%20and%20the%20BJP's%20Tamil%20Nadu%20chief%2C%20Annamalai%2C%20who%20added%20dramatic%20flair%20by%20flogging%20himself.%20All%20these%20actions%20seemed%20to%20align%20with%20a%20common%20strategy%20designed%20to%20embarrass%20the%20DMK%20on%20an%20emotive%20law-and-order%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Common%20Agenda%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20the%20AIADMK%2C%20the%20TVK%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20mirrored%20each%20other's%20stance%20by%20boycotting%20the%20upcoming%20by-election%20for%20the%20Erode%20East%20constituency%2C%20scheduled%20for%20February%205.%20While%20the%20AIADMK%20and%20the%20BJP%20accused%20the%20DMK%20of%20manipulating%20the%20elections%20through%20muscle%20power%2C%20Vijay%20criticised%20the%20ruling%20party%20for%20making%20a%20mockery%20of%20the%20by-election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20evident%20that%20the%20three%20parties%20share%20a%20common%20agenda%20to%20unseat%20the%20DMK%2C%20but%20the%20timing%20and%20their%20collective%20stance%20on%20the%20sexual%20assault%20case%20and%20the%20by-election%20hint%20at%20some%20behind-the-scenes%20coordination.%20While%20this%20was%20expected%2C%20the%20key%20question%20remains%3A%20can%20this%20coordination%20mature%20into%20a%20formal%20alliance%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20fundamental%20stumbling%20blocks.%20First%2C%20who%20will%20be%20the%20lead%20player%20in%20such%20an%20alliance%3F%20Can%20the%20AIADMK%2C%20as%20the%20principal%20opposition%20party%2C%20accept%20Vijay%20as%20an%20equal%E2%80%94or%20at%20least%20a%20near-equal%E2%80%94in%20terms%20of%20seats%3F%20If%20not%2C%20can%20Vijay%2C%20with%20his%20star%20power%2C%20agree%20to%20play%20the%20junior%20partner%3F%20Second%2C%20can%20they%20incorporate%20the%20BJP%20into%20the%20alliance%2C%20given%20the%20realities%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20electorate%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20AIADMK%20Needs%20New%20Friends%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AIADMK%20needs%20fresh%20energy.%20And%2C%20after%20decisively%20losing%20three%20successive%20elections%E2%80%942019%2C%202021%2C%20and%202024%E2%80%94it%20absolutely%20needs%20to%20win%20the%202026%20assembly%20polls.%20Given%20the%20formidable%20alliance%20the%20DMK%20has%20led%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20Congress%2C%20left%20parties%20and%20other%20smaller%20groups%2C%20the%20AIADMK%2C%20under%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Edappadi%20K.%20Palaniswami%2C%20knows%20that%20an%20alliance%20with%20Vijay%20could%20be%20essential%20to%20gaining%20momentum.%20From%20Vijay's%20perspective%20too%2C%20going%20it%20alone%20could%20be%20a%20huge%20risk%2C%20potentially%20leading%20to%20decent%20vote%20shares%20but%20no%20seats.%20Additionally%2C%20if%20he%20contests%20independently%20and%20turns%20the%20election%20into%20a%20three-way%20race%2C%20he%20could%20end%20up%20splitting%20the%20anti-DMK%20vote%2C%20which%20would%20benefit%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20these%20dynamics%2C%20both%20sides%20may%20push%20hard%20to%20reach%20an%20agreement.%20It%20eventually%20may%20be%20one%20where%20the%20AIADMK%20remains%20the%20senior%20partner%20but%20offers%20a%20large%20share%20of%20seats%20to%20the%20TVK%20as%20it%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20concede%20too%20much%20on%20its%20dominant%20role.%20But%20they%20may%20have%20to%20leave%20the%20question%20of%20the%20Chief%20Ministerial%20face%20for%20post-poll%20calculations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20And%20The%20DMK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExcept%20in%20specific%20pockets%2C%20the%20BJP%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20marginal%20force%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20facing%20tough%20realities.%20A%20large%20minority%20vote%20and%20a%20strong%20ideological%2C%20regional%2C%20and%20linguistic%20narrative%20centred%20on%20Dravidian%20politics%20make%20it%20difficult%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20make%20significant%20inroads.%20Within%20the%20AIADMK%2C%20there%20are%20sizable%20factions%20wary%20of%20an%20alliance%20with%20it%2C%20and%20Actor%20Vijay%2C%20whose%20following%20includes%20many%20minority%20groups%2C%20would%20also%20be%20hesitant%20to%20form%20an%20open%20alliance%20with%20the%20party.%20In%20many%20ways%2C%20the%20Dravidian%20realities%20for%20the%20BJP%20haven't%20changed%20much%E2%80%94at%20least%20not%20yet.%20However%2C%20Vijay%20and%20the%20AIADMK%20are%20also%20aware%20that%20they%20will%20need%20the%20backing%20of%20the%20Centre%20to%20challenge%20the%20DMK's%20election%20machinery%20and%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20several%20respects%2C%20the%20dominance%20of%20the%20DMK%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20is%20comparable%20to%20the%20dominance%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20India.%20A%20cohesive%20and%20strategic%20alliance%20is%20essential%20to%20challenge%20it%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20gives%20all%20parties%20a%20strong%20incentive%20to%20navigate%20these%20tricky%20issues.%20It's%20clear%20that%20backroom%20managers%20are%20working%20to%20stitch%20an%20alliance%20together%2C%20and%20if%20it%20solidifies%2C%20smaller%20players%20may%20also%20be%20drawn%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20Executive%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%