rump%20however%20plans%20to%20%26quot%3Bappeal%20it%26quot%3B.%20What%20exactly%20is%20the%20controversy%20and%20how%20will%20it%20impact%20Indians%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E14th%20Amendment%20Of%20The%20US%20Constitution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2020%2C%20following%20the%20inaugural%20ceremony%2C%2047th%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20signed%20a%20series%20of%20executive%20orders%2C%20including%20restricting%20automatic%20birthright%20citizenship.%20This%20order%20specifically%20focuses%20on%20the%2014th%20Amendment%20which%20states%3A%20%26quot%3BAll%20persons%20born%20or%20naturalized%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20subject%20to%20the%20jurisdiction%20thereof%2C%20are%20citizens%20of%20the%20United%20States%20and%20of%20the%20State%20wherein%20they%20reside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20anyone%20born%20in%20the%20US%20is%20considered%20a%20citizen%20at%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fpresidential-actions%2F2025%2F01%2Fprotecting-the-meaning-and-value-of-american-citizenship%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexecutive%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20interprets%20this%20amendment%20differently.%20It%20states%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bprivilege%20of%20United%20States%20citizenship%20does%20not%20automatically%20extend%20to%20persons%20born%20in%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildren%20born%20to%20undocumented%20parents%20are%20not%20entitled%20to%20automatic%20birthright%20citizenship%2C%20as%20per%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBorn%20In%20The%20US%20But%20Not%20A%20Citizen%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fpresidential-actions%2F2025%2F01%2Fprotecting-the-meaning-and-value-of-american-citizenship%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexecutive%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20categories%20of%20individuals%20born%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20not%20subject%20to%20citizenship%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20that%20person's%20mother%20was%20unlawfully%20present%20in%20the%20US%20and%20the%20father%20was%20not%20a%20US%20citizen%20or%20lawful%20permanent%20resident%20at%20the%20time%20of%20said%20person's%20birth%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20that%20person's%20mother's%20presence%20in%20the%20US%20at%20the%20time%20of%20said%20person's%20birth%20was%20lawful%20but%20temporary%20and%20the%20father%20was%20not%20a%20US%20citizen%20or%20lawful%20permanent%20resident%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhom%20Does%20Trump's%20Executive%20Order%20Apply%20To%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20interpretation%20of%20the%2014th%20Amendment%20shall%20apply%20only%20to%20persons%20who%20are%20born%20within%20the%20US%20after%2030%20days%20from%20the%20date%20of%20the%20order%20that%20is%20after%20February%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%201.5%20lakh%20newborn%20children%20would%20be%20denied%20citizenship%20annually%20if%20Trump's%20order%20is%20allowed%20to%20stand%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Democratic-led%20states%2C%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fblatantly-unconstitutional-judge-blocks-trump-citizenship-order-7544238%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Does%20It%20Affect%20Indians%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20families%20using%20birth%20tourism%20as%20a%20means%20to%20obtain%20US%20citizenship%20will%20be%20largely%20impacted%20by%20Trump's%20order%20if%20it%20comes%20into%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBirth%20tourism%20is%20a%20practice%20of%20travelling%20to%20the%20US%20or%20other%20developed%20nations%20to%20give%20birth%20there%20so%20that%20the%20newborn%20becomes%20a%20citizen%20of%20the%20said%20country%20by%20birth.%20It%20is%20a%20way%20for%20families%20to%20seek%20better%20educational%2C%20career%20and%20health%20opportunities%20for%20their%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcarnegieendowment.org%2Fresearch%2F2024%2F10%2Findian-american-voters-election-survey-us%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECarnegie%20Endowment%20for%20International%20Peace%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%205.2%20million%20people%20of%20Indian%20origin%20reside%20in%20the%20US.%20Indian%20Americans%20are%20the%20second%20largest%20immigrant%20group%20in%20the%20US%2C%20it%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fohss.dhs.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2024-06%2F2024_0418_ohss_estimates-of-the-unauthorized-immigrant-population-residing-in-the-united-states-january-2018%2525E2%252580%252593january-2022.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%20published%20last%20year%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%3C%2Fa%3E%20estimated%20some%202.2%20lakh%20unauthorised%20Indian%20immigrants%20resided%20in%20the%20US%20as%20of%202022.%20It%20is%20less%20than%20half%20of%204.8%20lakh%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737699780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F1tugp9q_donald-trump_625x300_24_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjudge-blocks-trumps-birthright-citizenship-order-what-it-means-for-indians-7546933%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20January%2020%2C%2047th%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20signed%20a%20series%20of%20executive%20orders%2C%20including%20restricting%20automatic%20birthright%20citizenship.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjudge-blocks-trumps-birthright-citizenship-order-what-it-means-for-indians-7546933%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Not%20Virus%20Or%20Bacteria%2C%20Here's%20What%20Caused%20%26quot%3BMystery%20Illness%26quot%3B%20In%20J%26amp%3BK's%20Rajouri%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExperts%20have%20found%20the%20cause%20behind%20the%20%26quot%3Bmystery%20illness%26quot%3B%20that%20has%20claimed%20at%20least%2017%20lives%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Rajouri.%20The%20deaths%20had%20sparked%20fear%20and%20panic%20in%20the%20Budhal%20village%20over%20the%20past%20month%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20central%20team%20being%20formed%20to%20probe%20the%20cause.%20Doctors%20had%20earlier%20ruled%20out%20any%20virus%20or%20bacterial%20presence%20in%20the%20samples.%20In%20the%20latest%20update%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Jitendra%20Singh%20told%20the%20media%20that%20the%20illness%20was%20due%20to%20cadmium%20toxin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20Dainik%20Jagran%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20cadmium%20was%20detected%20in%20the%20bodies%20of%20the%20victims%20during%20the%20tests%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Toxicology%20Research%2C%20Lucknow.%20How%20cadmium%20found%20its%20way%20inside%20the%20body%20is%20still%20a%20matter%20of%20investigation%2C%20he%20said%2C%20clarifying%20no%20other%20virus%2C%20bacteria%2C%20or%20infection%20was%20found%20in%20the%20victims'%20samples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsrinagar-news%2Fspecial-team-to-probe-child-deaths-in-rajouri-due-to-mysterious-illness-7486443%5C%22%3ESpecial%20Team%20To%20Probe%2015%20Deaths%20In%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir's%20Rajouri%20Due%20To%20Mysterious%20Illness%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20any%20mischief%2C%20then%20we%20will%20know%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECadmium%20is%20a%20highly%20toxic%20metal%20that%20can%20cause%20several%20ailments%20if%20it%20finds%20its%20way%20inside%20the%20body.%20Cadmium%20poisoning%20can%20occur%20due%20to%20polluted%20air%20or%20consumption%20of%20contaminated%20food%20and%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20a%20team%20of%20health%20experts%20said%20that%20the%20deaths%20were%20caused%20by%20neurotoxins.%20The%20victims%20had%20a%20common%20medical%20condition%20-%20brain%20swelling%20or%20edema%2C%20Dr%20AS%20Bhatia%2C%20principal%20of%20Government%20Medical%20College%20(GMC)%2C%20Rajouri%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20samples%20were%20tested%20at%20top%20laboratories%2C%20including%20the%20National%20Centre%20for%20Disease%20Control%20(NCDC)%20and%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Virology%2C%20Pune%2C%20which%20showed%20the%20presence%20of%20neurotoxins%20that%20resulted%20in%20brain%20damage%2C%20according%20to%20Dr%20Bhatia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20try%20to%20mitigate%20the%20problem%20of%20patients%20reporting%20with%20brain%20damage%2C%20but%20once%20the%20patient%20reports%20with%20serious%20brain%20damage%2C%20we%20cannot%20reverse%20the%20condition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said%2C%20assuring%20that%20the%20health%20department%20was%20actively%20monitoring%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EContainment%20Zone%2C%20Quarantine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajouri%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20battle%20the%20%26quot%3Bmysterious%20illness%26quot%3B%20since%20early%20December.%20The%2017%20deaths%2C%20including%2014%20children%2C%20from%20three%20families%20had%20the%20centre%20and%20state%20authorities%20scrambling%20to%20find%20an%20answer.%20Six%20more%20teenagers%2C%20including%20three%20siblings%2C%20have%20fallen%20ill%20in%20the%20last%20two%20days%20and%20are%20being%20kept%20in%20isolation%20wards%20at%20GMC%2C%20Rajouri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20have%20quarantined%20over%20200%20people%20who%20had%20come%20into%20contact%20with%20the%20victims'%20families.%20The%20close%20contacts%20from%20Budhal%20were%20shifted%20to%20the%20Nursing%20College%2C%20Rajouri%20for%20better%20preventive%20care%20on%20DC%20Abhishek%20Sharma's%20directions%2C%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEntire%20Budhal%20has%20been%20declared%20a%20containment%20zone%20and%20the%20district%20administration%20has%20set%20up%20facilities%20for%20families%20who%20were%20relocated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGMC%20Rajouri%20has%20also%20strengthened%20its%20arrangements%20with%20five%20more%20child%20specialities%20and%20five%20anaesthesia%20specialists%20being%20put%20on%20duty.%20All%20types%20of%20advanced%20technology%20are%20there%20to%20handle%20any%20emergency%2C%20confirmed%20Dr%20Bhatia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20visited%20Rajouri%20earlier%20this%20week%20and%20assured%20the%20citizens%20that%20the%20central%20and%20state%20authorities%20are%20trying%20to%20find%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20inter-ministerial%20team%20was%20formed%20by%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20last%20week%20to%20probe%20the%20unexplained%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737699720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fcc9dnbsg_rajouri-deaths_625x300_24_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhats-behind-mystery-illness-that-claimed-17-lives-in-j-k-doctors-answer-7546638%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Doctors%20have%20found%20the%20cause%20behind%20the%20%26quot%3Bmystery%20illness%26quot%3B%20that%20has%20claimed%20at%20least%2017%20lives%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Rajouri.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhats-behind-mystery-illness-that-claimed-17-lives-in-j-k-doctors-answer-7546638%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Big%20B%3A%20Shashi's%20Deewaar%20performance%20was%20understated%20-%20Exclusive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737699528000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117510232%2Cimgsize-50932.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Famitabh-bachchan-i-dont-think-deewaar-would-have-be