01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-3-1737031987.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-3-1737031987-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-3-1737031987-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-3-1737031987-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-3-1737031987-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-398461%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENearly%2042%20government%20and%20private%20clinics%20are%20offering%20up%20to%20three%20free%20ultrasound%20scans%20to%20pregnant%20women.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20backbone%20of%20this%20scheme%20is%20the%20Nirikhyana%20app%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Berhampur%20Sub-Collector%20Dheenah%20Dastageer%20IAS%2C%20stressing%20its%20role%20in%20overcoming%20socioeconomic%20barriers%20and%20the%20digital%20divide.%20She%20also%20assisted%20the%20team%20in%20designing%20the%20mobile%20app%20and%20its%20implementation%20at%20the%20grassroots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20follows%20a%20three-module%20approach%20that%20allows%20Auxiliary%20Nurse%20Midwives%20(ANMs)%20to%20register%20pregnant%20women%20on%20the%20Nirikhyana%20mobile%20app%2C%20facilitating%20consultations%20with%20doctors%20who%20can%20then%20refer%20cases%20to%20nearby%20ultrasound%20clinics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDibyajyoti%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20s