%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-30-at-15.58.43-1737031873.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-30-at-15.58.43-1737031873.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-30-at-15.58.43-1737031873-300x134.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-30-at-15.58.43-1737031873-500x223.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-30-at-15.58.43-1737031873-768x343.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-30-at-15.58.43-1737031873-1200x536.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-30-at-15.58.43-1737031873-150x67.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-398453%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22572%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20scheme%2C%20less%20than%2030%20percent%20of%20registered%20pregnant%20women%20would%20undergo%20USG%20tests.%20This%20number%20has%20increased%20to%20128.6%20percent%20post%20the%20launch.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20high-risk%20pregnancy%20detection%20has%20also%20increased%20from%204%20to%2025%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20intervention%2C%20the%20maternal%20mortality%20rate%20(MMR)%20has%20reduced%20from%2097%20in%202021-22%20to%2069%20in%202023-24.%20In%20the%20same%20period%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F202538%2Fbengaluru-startup-medical-tech-solution-pregnancy-maternal-mortality-rate-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eneonatal%20mortality%20rate%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20reduced%20from%2018%20to%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%